sequenceDiagram
    actor A as Administrator
    participant FE as React<br/>DemoPage
    participant API1 as DRF<br/>DemoStartView
    participant API2 as DRF<br/>DemoClearView
    participant API3 as DRF<br/>DemoStatusView
    participant Perm as IsAdmin
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    A->>FE: Check demo status
    FE->>API3: GET /api/demo/status/
    API3->>DB: Alert.objects.filter(is_demo=True).exists()
    DB-->>API3: Demo data status
    API3-->>FE: 200 OK {has_demo_data: false}
    A->>FE: Click "Start Demo" with scenario config
    FE->>API1: POST /api/demo/start/
    API1->>Perm: has_permission(request)
    Perm-->>API1: Allowed (Admin)
    API1->>API1: Generate ATTACK_PROFILES with SOURCE_IPS
    API1->>DB: Bulk create demo Alert objects
    API1->>API1: _fanout_demo_alerts() to all tier DBs
    API1-->>FE: 200 OK {alerts_created: 50}
    FE-->>U: Display demo summary
    Note over A,FE: After demo showcase
    A->>FE: Click "Clear Demo Data"
    FE->>API2: POST /api/demo/clear/
    API2->>DB: Alert.objects.filter(is_demo=True).delete()
    DB-->>API2: Demo data cleared
    API2-->>FE: 200 OK "Demo data cleared"
    FE-->>U: Demo data removed confirmation
